  <p class=3DMsoNormal><span lang=3DEN-GB style=3D'mso-ansi-language:EN-GB;
  mso-no-proof:yes'>Resource Extractors enable mining of resources from
  planets, moons, asteroids or gas clouds. These components are typically b=
uilt
  into mining stations or mining ships.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal><span lang=3DEN-GB style=3D'mso-ansi-language:EN-GB;
  mso-no-proof:yes'>Note that ships or bases must be stationary to use reso=
urce
  extractors.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal><span lang=3DEN-GB style=3D'mso-ansi-language:EN-GB;
  mso-no-proof:yes'>Standard extractors mine metal ores, coal, silicon,
  petroleum and gemstones. More specialized gas extractors collect gases.
  Luxury resource extractors enable collection of luxury resources.<o:p></o=
:p></span></p>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal><span lang=3DEN-GB style=3D'mso-ansi-language:EN-GB;
  mso-no-proof:yes'>Note that colonies extract resources by themselves, wit=
hout
  the need for extraction components on mining stations or mining ships</sp=
an>.<span
  lang=3DEN-GB style=3D'mso-ansi-language:EN-GB'><o:p></o:p></span></p>
